Move benchmark artifacts

Output the artifacts to the root of the repository.

Simplify benchmarks name

Remove "Benchmarks" suffix.

Add more benchmarks

- Add benchmarks for rendering the homepage and the version.
- Refactor benchmarks to move server to its own class.

Remove web SDK from benchmarks

Remove the web SDK from the benchmarks project so that the artifact directory is not overridden.

Remove redundant files (#1912)

- Remove files that are now served from CDN.
- Update favicon.ico.

Benchmark .NET vNext

- Run benchmarks for pushes to the vNext branches.
- Remove concurrency.

Link to branch

Link to the specific branch in the workflow summary.

Add Sentry (#2316)

Add Sentry error reporting.

Fix container deployment

Ensure that libcurl native libraries are present in the container image.

Fix Sentry

Add libnghttp2 to the container image.

Install libnghttp2-dev (#2331)

Install `libnghttp2-dev` so that `libnghttp2` is present on the container to be copied into the container image for use with Sentry native.

Set LD_PRELOAD

Set `LD_PRELOAD` in the container so that `libnghttp2` can be found.

Install libidn2-dev

Install `libidn2-dev` to make `libidn2` available to the container.

Install libunistring-dev

- Install `libunistring-dev` so that `libunistring.so` is installed in the container.
- Update `LD_PRELOAD` to include `libidn2` and `libunistring`.

Install librtmp-dev

Install `librtmp-dev` to make `librtmp` available in the container.

Install libgnutls28-dev

Install `libgnutls28-dev` so that `libgnutls` is available to the container.

Remove Sentry

It's too much work trying to work out all the `.so` files needed to deploy to the chiseled container, so just remove until Sentry native can be opted-out of.

Add test analytics

Use Codecov's test analytics feature.

Update humans.txt

Switch from Twitter to Bluesky.
